---
layout: base.njk
title: Oikos – Bouwend Bureau | Den Haag
description: Duurzame renovatie met hennepvezels. Wij maken woningen klaar voor 2050.
---

<!-- ===== HERO ===== -->
<section id="home" class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <img src="/assets/img/oikos-10.jpg" alt="Oikos project" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
    <div class="hero-overlay absolute inset-0"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-32">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <p class="text-oikos-green font-bold tracking-widest uppercase text-xs mb-5">
        Oikos – Bouwend Bureau &nbsp;·&nbsp; Den Haag
      </p>
      <h1 class="text-white text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold leading-tight mb-6">
        Wij maken jouw woning klaar voor&nbsp;2050
      </h1>
      <p class="text-gray-300 text-xl leading-relaxed mb-10">
        Duurzame renovatie met hennepvezels. Betaalbaar, gezond en toekomstbestendig —
        met behoud van het karakter van je woning.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="#projecten" class="bg-oikos-green hover:bg-oikos-green-dark text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold transition-colors">Bekijk onze projecten</a>
        <a href="#over-ons"  class="border-2 border-white/70 text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-oikos-dark px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold transition-all">Over Oikos</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 text-white/50 flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
    <span class="text-xs tracking-widest uppercase">Scroll</span>
    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 animate-bounce" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== USP BAR ===== -->
<section class="bg-oikos-dark py-8">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-white">
      <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-oikos-green flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div><p class="font-semibold leading-tight">Volledig natuurlijk</p><p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Hennepvezels als isolatiemateriaal</p></div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-white">
      <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-oikos-green flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div><p class="font-semibold leading-tight">Luchtdicht bouwen</p><p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Minimaal energieverbruik</p></div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-white">
      <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-oikos-green flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div><p class="font-semibold leading-tight">Karakter behouden</p><p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Renovatie met respect voor de woning</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== OVER ONS ===== -->
<section id="over-ons" class="py-28 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
      <div>
        <span class="section-tag">Over Oikos</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-oikos-dark leading-tight mb-6">Een bouwend bureau met een missie</h2>
        <p class="text-oikos-gray text-lg leading-relaxed mb-5">
          Oikos is een bouwend bureau gevestigd in Den Haag. We specialiseren ons in duurzame renovatie van bestaande woningen, met bijzondere aandacht voor isolatie met hennepvezels en luchtdicht bouwen.
        </p>
        <p class="text-oikos-gray text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10">
          We geloven dat duurzaam wonen niet ten koste hoeft te gaan van comfort of het karakter van een woning. Met de juiste materialen en aanpak wordt een woning warmer, gezonder én toekomstbestendiger.
        </p>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <img src="/assets/logo-hart.png" alt="Oikos hart" class="h-12 w-12" />
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-oikos-dark">Guido Bouwman</p>
            <p class="text-oikos-gray text-sm">Oprichter – Oikos, Bouwend Bureau</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="relative">
        <img src="/assets/img/oikos-21.jpg" alt="Guido Bouwman aan het werk" class="w-full rounded-2xl object-cover shadow-2xl aspect-[4/3]" />
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 bg-oikos-green text-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl">
          <p class="text-4xl font-extrabold leading-none">2050</p>
          <p class="text-sm mt-1 text-white/85">Klaar voor de toekomst</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== DIENSTEN ===== -->
<section id="diensten" class="py-28 bg-oikos-green-light">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="section-tag">Wat wij doen</span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-oikos-dark">Onze diensten</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 card-hover shadow-sm">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-oikos-green-light rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-7 w-7 text-oikos-green" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-oikos-dark mb-3">Isolatie met hennepvezels</h3>
        <p class="text-oikos-gray leading-relaxed text-sm">Wanden, vloeren en daken isoleren met hennepvezelplaten. Ademend, duurzaam en CO₂-negatief materiaal dat het binnenklimaat sterk verbetert.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 card-hover shadow-sm">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-oikos-green-light rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-7 w-7 text-oikos-green" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-oikos-dark mb-3">Luchtdicht bouwen</h3>
        <p class="text-oikos-gray leading-relaxed text-sm">Een goed geïsoleerde woning staat of valt met luchtdichtheid. Wij brengen dampopen folie en afdichtingstape professioneel aan voor optimale resultaten.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 card-hover shadow-sm">
        <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-oikos-green-light rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-7 w-7 text-oikos-green" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-oikos-dark mb-3">Duurzame renovatie</h3>
        <p class="text-oikos-gray leading-relaxed text-sm">Van ontwerp tot uitvoering: we begeleiden het volledige renovatieproces. Behoud van het karakter van de woning staat daarbij altijd voorop.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== HENNEPVEZELS ===== -->
<section id="materiaal" class="py-28 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <img src="/assets/img/oikos-2.jpg" alt="Hennepvezel plafond"  class="rounded-2xl object-cover w-full aspect-square shadow-md" />
        <img src="/assets/img/oikos-5.jpg" alt="Hennepvezel detail"   class="rounded-2xl object-cover w-full aspect-square shadow-md mt-8" />
        <img src="/assets/img/oikos-3.jpg" alt="Isolatieplaten"       class="rounded-2xl object-cover w-full aspect-square shadow-md" />
        <img src="/assets/img/oikos-4.jpg" alt="Dampopen folie"       class="rounded-2xl object-cover w-full aspect-square shadow-md mt-8" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <span class="section-tag">Het materiaal</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-oikos-dark leading-tight mb-6">Waarom hennepvezels?</h2>
        <p class="text-oikos-gray text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
          Hennepvezels zijn een van de meest duurzame isolatiematerialen die er bestaan. De plant groeit snel, bindt CO₂ en vergt geen pesticiden. Als isolatiemateriaal is het ademend, brandvertragend en vochtregulerend.
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-4">
          {% set punten = [
            ["CO₂-negatief", "de plant slaat meer koolstof op dan er bij productie vrijkomt"],
            ["Ademend materiaal", "voorkomt condensatie en schimmelvorming"],
            ["Uitstekende Rc-waarde", "hoge thermische weerstand bij relatief geringe dikte"],
            ["100% biologisch afbreekbaar", "geen microplastics, geen schadelijke stoffen"]
          ] %}
          {% for punt in punten %}
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-oikos-green flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-3.5 w-3.5 text-white" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
            </div>
            <p class="text-oikos-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">
              <strong class="text-oikos-dark">{{ punt[0] }}</strong> — {{ punt[1] }}
            </p>
          </li>
          {% endfor %}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== PROJECTEN ===== -->
<section id="projecten" class="py-28 bg-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="section-tag">Ons werk</span>
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-oikos-dark">Projecten</h2>
      <p class="text-oikos-gray mt-4 text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto">Een selectie van renovaties waarbij we hennepvezelisolatie en luchtdicht bouwen hebben toegepast.</p>
    </div>
    {% set projecten = [
      ["oikos-10.jpg", "Wand- & plafondisolatie"],
      ["oikos-1.jpg",  "Luchtdichte wandopbouw"],
      ["oikos-6.jpg",  "Hennepvezelplaten"],
      ["oikos-15.jpg", "Renovatie Den Haag"],
      ["oikos-20.jpg", "Dampopen folie SIGA Majrex"],
      ["oikos-1b.jpg", "Klaar voor 2050"]
    ] %}
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      {% for p in projecten %}
      <div class="relative group overflow-hidden rounded-2xl aspect-square">
        <img src="/assets/img/{{ p[0] }}" alt="{{ p[1] }}" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" />
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-oikos-dark/50 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 flex items-end p-4">
          <p class="text-white font-semibold text-sm">{{ p[1] }}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===== NIEUWS – 11ty blog loop ===== -->
<section id="nieuws" class="py-28 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="flex items-end justify-between mb-16">
      <div>
        <span class="section-tag">Updates</span>
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-oikos-dark">Laatste nieuws</h2>
      </div>
      <a href="/nieuws/" class="text-oikos-green hover:text-oikos-green-dark font-semibold text-sm flex items-center gap-2 transition-colors">
        Alle berichten
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>

    {%- set recentePosts = collections.post | reverse | limit(3) -%}
    {% if recentePosts.length > 0 %}
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      {% for post in recentePosts %}
      <article class="card-hover group cursor-pointer">
        <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="block">
          <div class="overflow-hidden rounded-2xl mb-5 aspect-video bg-oikos-green-light">
            {% if post.data.image %}
            <img src="{{ post.data.image }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}" class="w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500" />
            {% else %}
            <div class="w-full h-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <img src="/assets/logo-hart.png" alt="Oikos" class="h-16 opacity-30" />
            </div>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
          <p class="text-oikos-green text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-2">
            {{ post.data.category or "Nieuws" }} · {{ post.date | dutchDate }}
          </p>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-oikos-dark mb-2 group-hover:text-oikos-green transition-colors leading-snug">
            {{ post.data.title }}
          </h3>
          <p class="text-oikos-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">
            {{ post.data.excerpt or post.templateContent | striptags | truncate(120) }}
          </p>
        </a>
      </article>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
    {% else %}
    <p class="text-oikos-gray text-center py-8 col-span-3">
      Er zijn nog geen nieuwsberichten. Voeg ze toe via <a href="/admin/" class="text-oikos-green underline">het admin-panel</a>.
    </p>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>
